[
    {
        "text": "Hi.",
        "start": 1.74,
        "duration": 0.377
    },
    {
        "text": "I'm Rebecca from engVid, and in this lesson\nyou're going to learn 10 easy questions",
        "start": 2.142,
        "duration": 5.81
    },
    {
        "text": "that you can use in all kinds\nof everyday situations.",
        "start": 7.977,
        "duration": 3.903
    },
    {
        "text": "Now, they are really easy so they will not\nonly help you to understand what people are",
        "start": 12.179,
        "duration": 5.701
    },
    {
        "text": "saying, but you can also\nstart to use them yourself.",
        "start": 17.88,
        "duration": 3.875
    },
    {
        "text": "Why?",
        "start": 22.008,
        "duration": 0.951
    },
    {
        "text": "Because all these questions\nhave only three words.",
        "start": 22.984,
        "duration": 4.589
    },
    {
        "text": "All right?",
        "start": 27.598,
        "duration": 0.778
    },
    {
        "text": "And I think, and I know, and I\nbelieve that you can learn them.",
        "start": 28.401,
        "duration": 5.186
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 33.612,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "So let's look at what they are.",
        "start": 34.637,
        "duration": 1.7
    },
    {
        "text": "Let's go.",
        "start": 36.59,
        "duration": 1.207
    },
    {
        "text": "Number one: \"What's the matter?\"",
        "start": 38.333,
        "duration": 2.99
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 41.348,
        "duration": 0.461
    },
    {
        "text": "If someone says:\n\"What's the matter?\"",
        "start": 42.14,
        "duration": 2.45
    },
    {
        "text": "it means: \"What's the problem?",
        "start": 44.801,
        "duration": 2.88
    },
    {
        "text": "What's...?",
        "start": 47.869,
        "duration": 0.445
    },
    {
        "text": "What's wrong?\"",
        "start": 48.339,
        "duration": 1.2
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 49.564,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Now, don't look on this side.",
        "start": 50.589,
        "duration": 2.16
    },
    {
        "text": "This is not the answer, this\nis not the explanation.",
        "start": 52.774,
        "duration": 3.481
    },
    {
        "text": "These we're going to use\nlater when we do our quiz.",
        "start": 56.28,
        "duration": 3.832
    },
    {
        "text": "So just listen to me to understand\nwhat the questions mean first of all.",
        "start": 60.137,
        "duration": 5.839
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 66.001,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "So: \"What's the matter?\"\nmeans: \"What's the problem?",
        "start": 67.026,
        "duration": 2.861
    },
    {
        "text": "What's wrong?\"",
        "start": 69.912,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Number two: \"Do you mind?\"",
        "start": 71.384,
        "duration": 2.407
    },
    {
        "text": "Now, when do we\nsay: \"Do you mind?\"",
        "start": 74.485,
        "duration": 1.998
    },
    {
        "text": "What does that mean?",
        "start": 76.511,
        "duration": 0.898
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Do you mind?\"",
        "start": 77.409,
        "duration": 1.238
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Do you mind?\"",
        "start": 78.71,
        "duration": 0.869
    },
    {
        "text": "means: \"Do you have\nany objection?",
        "start": 79.579,
        "duration": 3.56
    },
    {
        "text": "Do you have any...?",
        "start": 83.164,
        "duration": 2.6
    },
    {
        "text": "Do you not agree with\nme for some reason?",
        "start": 85.789,
        "duration": 3.04
    },
    {
        "text": "Do you not accept what\nI'm about to do?\"",
        "start": 88.854,
        "duration": 4.409
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Do you mind?\" means:",
        "start": 93.543,
        "duration": 0.931
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Do you have any problem with what I'm going\nto do, or say?\" or something like that.",
        "start": 94.499,
        "duration": 5.106
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 99.63,
        "duration": 0.834
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Do you mind?\"",
        "start": 100.489,
        "duration": 1.649
    },
    {
        "text": "Number three: \"Have you heard?\"",
        "start": 102.499,
        "duration": 2.411
    },
    {
        "text": "Now, some of these are full\ngrammatical questions.",
        "start": 105.705,
        "duration": 4.097
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 109.827,
        "duration": 0.686
    },
    {
        "text": "For example: \"What's the matter?\" is\ncompletely and grammatically correct.",
        "start": 110.538,
        "duration": 4.14
    },
    {
        "text": "Some of them that you'll see down here are\nactually just shortened versions of a fuller",
        "start": 114.703,
        "duration": 6.07
    },
    {
        "text": "question, but because they're used\nso often people do shorten them.",
        "start": 120.798,
        "duration": 4.379
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 125.202,
        "duration": 0.588
    },
    {
        "text": "So keep that in mind also.",
        "start": 125.815,
        "duration": 1.709
    },
    {
        "text": "So: \"Have you heard?\"",
        "start": 127.549,
        "duration": 2.191
    },
    {
        "text": "If somebody just says:\n\"Have you heard?\"",
        "start": 129.74,
        "duration": 2.921
    },
    {
        "text": "why would they say that?",
        "start": 132.911,
        "duration": 1.041
    },
    {
        "text": "Have you heard what?",
        "start": 133.977,
        "duration": 1.32
    },
    {
        "text": "So in what situation\ndo we use this?",
        "start": 135.322,
        "duration": 3.157
    },
    {
        "text": "Usually people will say: \"Have you heard?\"\nwhen there's some sort of big news.",
        "start": 138.504,
        "duration": 6.277
    },
    {
        "text": "Now, it could be big news in terms of world\nnews, it could be big news in terms of in",
        "start": 144.976,
        "duration": 5.464
    },
    {
        "text": "your office, it could be big\nnews in terms of your family.",
        "start": 150.44,
        "duration": 5.005
    },
    {
        "text": "But whatever it is, it is considered by the\nperson who's asking you this to be big news",
        "start": 155.47,
        "duration": 7.445
    },
    {
        "text": "that you either probably have heard about\nand do know about, or should know about.",
        "start": 162.94,
        "duration": 6.115
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 169.08,
        "duration": 0.655
    },
    {
        "text": "So then the person asks\nyou: \"Have you heard?\"",
        "start": 169.76,
        "duration": 3.42
    },
    {
        "text": "And if you say: \"No. Why? What?",
        "start": 173.354,
        "duration": 2.126
    },
    {
        "text": "What are you talking about?\"\nthen they tell you.",
        "start": 175.505,
        "duration": 2.118
    },
    {
        "text": "And if you do know, then you\nsay: \"Yes, I know, I heard.\"",
        "start": 177.648,
        "duration": 3.167
    },
    {
        "text": "if it's bad news.",
        "start": 180.84,
        "duration": 0.838
    },
    {
        "text": "Or: \"Yes. I heard. She\nwon the lottery. Wow.\"",
        "start": 181.703,
        "duration": 2.76
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 184.488,
        "duration": 0.785
    },
    {
        "text": "So it could be good\nnews or bad news.",
        "start": 185.298,
        "duration": 2.601
    },
    {
        "text": "Next...",
        "start": 188.411,
        "duration": 0.649
    },
    {
        "text": "Of course the way they'll\nask the question will vary.",
        "start": 189.325,
        "duration": 2.605
    },
    {
        "text": "If they say: \"Have you heard?\"",
        "start": 191.93,
        "duration": 1.226
    },
    {
        "text": "that's good news.",
        "start": 193.181,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "They say: \"Have you heard?\"",
        "start": 194.206,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "that's not so good news.",
        "start": 195.45,
        "duration": 2.248
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay.",
        "start": 197.723,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "The next one: \"Care\nfor another?\"",
        "start": 198.748,
        "duration": 2.25
    },
    {
        "text": "Again, this is one of those\nwhere we're shortening it.",
        "start": 201.43,
        "duration": 3.326
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 204.781,
        "duration": 0.694
    },
    {
        "text": "So: \"Care for another?\"",
        "start": 205.5,
        "duration": 1.411
    },
    {
        "text": "Another what?",
        "start": 206.936,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Well, it depends\non the situation.",
        "start": 207.961,
        "duration": 2.36
    },
    {
        "text": "Usually we're talking\nabout food or drink.",
        "start": 210.346,
        "duration": 2.66
    },
    {
        "text": "So somebody might be saying:\n\"Care for another drink?\"",
        "start": 213.031,
        "duration": 3.147
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Care for\" means: \"Would you like?\nDo you want?\"",
        "start": 216.203,
        "duration": 4.02
    },
    {
        "text": "So: \"Do you want\nanother drink?\",",
        "start": 220.473,
        "duration": 1.983
    },
    {
        "text": "or \"Do you want another\npiece of cake?\",",
        "start": 222.755,
        "duration": 2.465
    },
    {
        "text": "or \"Do you want\nanother dessert?\",",
        "start": 225.245,
        "duration": 1.961
    },
    {
        "text": "or \"Do you want another\nslice of pizza?\"",
        "start": 227.231,
        "duration": 2.427
    },
    {
        "text": "So somebody might just\nsay: \"Care for another?\"",
        "start": 229.683,
        "duration": 2.96
    },
    {
        "text": "instead of saying: \"Do you\nwant another something?\"",
        "start": 232.668,
        "duration": 2.776
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 235.469,
        "duration": 1.12
    },
    {
        "text": "And the last one here\nis: \"Who is it?\"",
        "start": 236.614,
        "duration": 2.3
    },
    {
        "text": "Now, that sounds pretty straightforward,\nbut in some languages we don't use...",
        "start": 239.31,
        "duration": 4.427
    },
    {
        "text": "They don't use \"it\" so much.",
        "start": 243.762,
        "duration": 2.21
    },
    {
        "text": "So when we're talking about: \"Who is it?\"\nare we talking about an animal or a thing?",
        "start": 245.997,
        "duration": 4.051
    },
    {
        "text": "No.",
        "start": 250.073,
        "duration": 0.623
    },
    {
        "text": "Because we said \"Who\", so\nwe're talking about people.",
        "start": 250.816,
        "duration": 2.86
    },
    {
        "text": "Usually this question we ask when let's\nsay somebody knocks on the door, we say:",
        "start": 253.746,
        "duration": 6.761
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Who is it?\"",
        "start": 260.532,
        "duration": 1.023
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 261.58,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Or let's say you have a phone call and\nsomebody else answers, and then you...",
        "start": 262.605,
        "duration": 5.47
    },
    {
        "text": "You ask...",
        "start": 268.1,
        "duration": 0.749
    },
    {
        "text": "They say: \"You have a call\",\nor \"You have a phone call.\"",
        "start": 268.874,
        "duration": 2.23
    },
    {
        "text": "And you say: \"Who is it?\"",
        "start": 271.129,
        "duration": 2.193
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 273.347,
        "duration": 0.726
    },
    {
        "text": "That means: \"Who is calling?\"\nor \"Who is at the door?\"",
        "start": 274.098,
        "duration": 3.307
    },
    {
        "text": "Depends on the situation.",
        "start": 277.43,
        "duration": 1.818
    },
    {
        "text": "All right.",
        "start": 279.273,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "So, let's review these five, and\nthen you can learn five more.",
        "start": 280.298,
        "duration": 5.85
    },
    {
        "text": "Let's do these.",
        "start": 286.308,
        "duration": 1.27
    },
    {
        "text": "So if somebody wants to say:\n\"Would you like another drink?\"",
        "start": 287.603,
        "duration": 5.904
    },
    {
        "text": "then what would they use?",
        "start": 293.532,
        "duration": 2.515
    },
    {
        "text": "Which expression could you\nuse for that meaning?",
        "start": 296.072,
        "duration": 4.37
    },
    {
        "text": "You would say: \"Care\nfor another?\"",
        "start": 300.501,
        "duration": 3.073
    },
    {
        "text": "Number four.",
        "start": 303.599,
        "duration": 2.154
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 305.778,
        "duration": 1.62
    },
    {
        "text": "If you want to ask\nsomebody: \"Who's calling?\"",
        "start": 307.423,
        "duration": 2.991
    },
    {
        "text": "what could you say?",
        "start": 310.56,
        "duration": 1.749
    },
    {
        "text": "You would say:",
        "start": 312.515,
        "duration": 1.313
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Who is it?\"",
        "start": 316.5,
        "duration": 1.228
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 317.753,
        "duration": 1.429
    },
    {
        "text": "If you want to say:\n\"What's wrong?\"",
        "start": 319.62,
        "duration": 4.071
    },
    {
        "text": "What's another way to\nsay: \"What's wrong?\"",
        "start": 323.716,
        "duration": 3.139
    },
    {
        "text": "Look at it.",
        "start": 327.494,
        "duration": 1.508
    },
    {
        "text": "Which one of these?",
        "start": 329.37,
        "duration": 1.549
    },
    {
        "text": "For: \"What's wrong?\"\nwe would usually say",
        "start": 331.482,
        "duration": 2.997
    },
    {
        "text": "number one: \"What's the matter?\"",
        "start": 334.504,
        "duration": 3.948
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 338.477,
        "duration": 0.795
    },
    {
        "text": "\"What's the matter?",
        "start": 339.297,
        "duration": 1.148
    },
    {
        "text": "What's the problem?",
        "start": 340.47,
        "duration": 1.83
    },
    {
        "text": "What's wrong?\"",
        "start": 342.3,
        "duration": 0.814
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 343.139,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Can I use this chair?\"",
        "start": 344.694,
        "duration": 2.116
    },
    {
        "text": "So you're asking somebody:\n\"Could I use this chair?\"",
        "start": 346.81,
        "duration": 3.06
    },
    {
        "text": "And what might you\nsay after that?",
        "start": 349.87,
        "duration": 2.34
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Is it okay with you?\"",
        "start": 352.381,
        "duration": 2.295
    },
    {
        "text": "What's another way to say: \"Is it okay\nwith you or do you have any objection?\"",
        "start": 354.871,
        "duration": 4.313
    },
    {
        "text": "We would say number two:",
        "start": 359.395,
        "duration": 2.295
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Do you mind?\"",
        "start": 362.733,
        "duration": 2.046
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 364.779,
        "duration": 0.872
    },
    {
        "text": "And the last one: \"Do you\nknow the latest news?",
        "start": 365.812,
        "duration": 5.117
    },
    {
        "text": "Do you know what happened?",
        "start": 371.084,
        "duration": 1.343
    },
    {
        "text": "What people are talking\nabout, what you should know?\"",
        "start": 373.099,
        "duration": 3.39
    },
    {
        "text": "That is number three:",
        "start": 376.514,
        "duration": 2.698
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Have you heard?\"",
        "start": 380.078,
        "duration": 1.471
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 381.68,
        "duration": 0.606
    },
    {
        "text": "Next we're going to do five more so that you can\nstart to use these easy and snappy questions.",
        "start": 382.311,
        "duration": 7.001
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay, number six:\n\"Leaving so soon?\"",
        "start": 389.437,
        "duration": 4.534
    },
    {
        "text": "So when do we say:\n\"Leaving so soon?\"",
        "start": 394.075,
        "duration": 2.539
    },
    {
        "text": "Again, this is one of those shortened questions,\nbecause the full question would probably be:",
        "start": 396.779,
        "duration": 4.471
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Are you...?\"",
        "start": 401.25,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Or: \"Why are you leaving so seen?\"\nor \"Are you leaving so soon?\"",
        "start": 402.275,
        "duration": 4.313
    },
    {
        "text": "But we just say:\n\"Leaving so soon?\"",
        "start": 406.613,
        "duration": 2.22
    },
    {
        "text": "So this is when somebody is leaving a situation\nearly, like maybe somebody's leaving a party",
        "start": 409.227,
        "duration": 8.103
    },
    {
        "text": "before it's over or somebody's leaving a dinner,\nor somebody's leaving a seminar or a conference,",
        "start": 417.33,
        "duration": 6.479
    },
    {
        "text": "and they're leaving a little bit\nearlier than it's supposed to end.",
        "start": 423.809,
        "duration": 3.7
    },
    {
        "text": "So you just ask, because you...",
        "start": 427.586,
        "duration": 1.765
    },
    {
        "text": "Usually you ask somebody you care about\nor you care about why they're leaving,",
        "start": 429.376,
        "duration": 4.772
    },
    {
        "text": "so you just say:\n\"Leaving so soon?\"",
        "start": 434.173,
        "duration": 1.946
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 436.144,
        "duration": 0.709
    },
    {
        "text": "Especially if it's more at...",
        "start": 436.878,
        "duration": 1.956
    },
    {
        "text": "In a personal situation.",
        "start": 439.068,
        "duration": 1.524
    },
    {
        "text": "All right?",
        "start": 440.617,
        "duration": 0.975
    },
    {
        "text": "Now, so somebody might say:",
        "start": 441.806,
        "duration": 1.65
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Yes. I have to catch a flight\",",
        "start": 443.481,
        "duration": 1.751
    },
    {
        "text": "or \"I have to get to bed early\",\nor something like that.",
        "start": 445.257,
        "duration": 2.963
    },
    {
        "text": "That would be the answer.",
        "start": 448.245,
        "duration": 1.287
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 449.557,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Now, number seven:\n\"Have you met?\"",
        "start": 450.582,
        "duration": 3.273
    },
    {
        "text": "So when do we say:\n\"Have you met?\"",
        "start": 454.3,
        "duration": 2.623
    },
    {
        "text": "This \"you\" is referring to usually\ntwo people, or two or more people.",
        "start": 457.024,
        "duration": 4.276
    },
    {
        "text": "So let's say you go into a\nsituation and there's...",
        "start": 461.3,
        "duration": 2.927
    },
    {
        "text": "Let's pretend right now there are two\nfriends, and you want to know...",
        "start": 464.252,
        "duration": 4.319
    },
    {
        "text": "You are friends of each of these people, but\nyou don't know if they know each other.",
        "start": 468.596,
        "duration": 4.151
    },
    {
        "text": "So when we say: \"Have you met?\" we're\nsaying: \"Do you know each other?",
        "start": 472.772,
        "duration": 4.45
    },
    {
        "text": "Have you had a chance\nto meet each other?\"",
        "start": 477.247,
        "duration": 2.596
    },
    {
        "text": "Right?",
        "start": 479.868,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "So... And if not, then you\nare going to introduce them.",
        "start": 480.893,
        "duration": 4.064
    },
    {
        "text": "All right?",
        "start": 484.982,
        "duration": 0.811
    },
    {
        "text": "So you start by saying:\n\"Have you met?\"",
        "start": 485.818,
        "duration": 2.35
    },
    {
        "text": "All right, there we go.",
        "start": 488.898,
        "duration": 1.794
    },
    {
        "text": "Now, the next one is\nreally interesting.",
        "start": 490.717,
        "duration": 3.478
    },
    {
        "text": "\"What's the scoop?\"",
        "start": 494.22,
        "duration": 1.701
    },
    {
        "text": "This question actually comes from the world\nof journalism, because in journalism when",
        "start": 496.114,
        "duration": 5.934
    },
    {
        "text": "a reporter gets the scoop it means he\ngets the story, he gets the latest story.",
        "start": 502.073,
        "duration": 6.759
    },
    {
        "text": "And every reporter wants to get the scoop and\nget their news out on their channel before",
        "start": 508.857,
        "duration": 6.157
    },
    {
        "text": "anyone else.",
        "start": 515.039,
        "duration": 1.081
    },
    {
        "text": "So, a scoop is like the story, the\nlatest news, the latest story.",
        "start": 516.12,
        "duration": 5.669
    },
    {
        "text": "So when you ask somebody: \"What's\nthe scoop?\" it means, like:",
        "start": 521.764,
        "duration": 2.789
    },
    {
        "text": "\"What happened?\nWhat's the latest?",
        "start": 524.578,
        "duration": 2.169
    },
    {
        "text": "What's happening\nor what happened?\"",
        "start": 526.781,
        "duration": 2.04
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 528.846,
        "duration": 0.692
    },
    {
        "text": "What's the scoop?",
        "start": 529.563,
        "duration": 1.312
    },
    {
        "text": "All right.",
        "start": 531.805,
        "duration": 0.875
    },
    {
        "text": "The next one, number\nnine: \"Do you follow?\"",
        "start": 533.047,
        "duration": 3.288
    },
    {
        "text": "Now, \"follow\" can have\ndifferent meanings.",
        "start": 536.827,
        "duration": 3.072
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Follow\" can mean that you\nwalk after somebody else.",
        "start": 539.924,
        "duration": 2.94
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 542.889,
        "duration": 0.644
    },
    {
        "text": "Somebody's following\nyou, let's say.",
        "start": 543.558,
        "duration": 1.735
    },
    {
        "text": "You don't want that to happen.",
        "start": 545.318,
        "duration": 1.615
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 546.958,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Somebody... When you're going home at night,\nyou don't want anybody going after you",
        "start": 547.983,
        "duration": 3.681
    },
    {
        "text": "or following you.",
        "start": 551.689,
        "duration": 1.152
    },
    {
        "text": "But this doesn't have\nanything to do with that.",
        "start": 552.866,
        "duration": 2.44
    },
    {
        "text": "This means: \"Do you understand?\"",
        "start": 555.68,
        "duration": 3.611
    },
    {
        "text": "Because \"to follow\" is also a mental activity,\nit means to understand what's happening.",
        "start": 559.316,
        "duration": 5.691
    },
    {
        "text": "So, for example, I could ask you: \"Do you\nfollow the meaning of these questions?",
        "start": 565.054,
        "duration": 7.073
    },
    {
        "text": "Do you understand?\"",
        "start": 572.152,
        "duration": 1.502
    },
    {
        "text": "Usually this is not going to\nbe asked in the beginning.",
        "start": 573.799,
        "duration": 2.94
    },
    {
        "text": "So let's say somebody's giving some instructions\nor giving a lesson and there are a number",
        "start": 576.974,
        "duration": 4.831
    },
    {
        "text": "of steps, in the middle,\nthey ask: \"Do you follow?",
        "start": 581.83,
        "duration": 4.679
    },
    {
        "text": "Do you follow?",
        "start": 586.534,
        "duration": 0.903
    },
    {
        "text": "Are you following?\"",
        "start": 587.515,
        "duration": 1.32
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 588.86,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "So that means: \"Do\nyou understand?\"",
        "start": 589.885,
        "duration": 2.998
    },
    {
        "text": "And the last one is a very interesting\nquestion, and that's: \"What's the catch?\"",
        "start": 593.393,
        "duration": 6.231
    },
    {
        "text": "So what do we mean by\nsaying: \"What's the catch?\"",
        "start": 599.649,
        "duration": 2.71
    },
    {
        "text": "Sometimes you hear about something\nand it sounds too good to be true.",
        "start": 602.384,
        "duration": 5.78
    },
    {
        "text": "Like, okay: \"You can...",
        "start": 608.336,
        "duration": 1.803
    },
    {
        "text": "We are giving you...\"",
        "start": 610.139,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "A company puts an ad in the newspaper and it\nsays: \"We are giving you a thousand dollars.\"",
        "start": 611.139,
        "duration": 5.683
    },
    {
        "text": "What?",
        "start": 617.204,
        "duration": 0.827
    },
    {
        "text": "That sounds really good.",
        "start": 618.056,
        "duration": 1.694
    },
    {
        "text": "But usually it's a little too good to be true,\nso then we might ask: \"What's the catch?\"",
        "start": 619.775,
        "duration": 7.081
    },
    {
        "text": "So maybe in this advertisement which said:\n\"We're giving you a thousand dollars\", in",
        "start": 626.881,
        "duration": 4.364
    },
    {
        "text": "small...",
        "start": 631.27,
        "duration": 0.567
    },
    {
        "text": "In small writing at the bottom it\nsaid: \"When you buy a house from us.\"",
        "start": 631.862,
        "duration": 5.211
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 637.098,
        "duration": 0.718
    },
    {
        "text": "So the catch, the hidden problem, the hidden\ncondition was that when you buy a house from",
        "start": 637.841,
        "duration": 7.81
    },
    {
        "text": "this company, they will give you a discount\nof a thousand dollars, so it's like they're",
        "start": 645.676,
        "duration": 4.979
    },
    {
        "text": "giving you a thousand dollars.",
        "start": 650.68,
        "duration": 1.9
    },
    {
        "text": "But: \"What's the catch?\"",
        "start": 652.58,
        "duration": 1.87
    },
    {
        "text": "means that when there's some sort of a situation\nthat sounds like it's ideal, and really lovely",
        "start": 654.45,
        "duration": 6.11
    },
    {
        "text": "and beautiful, but there's some hidden\ndisadvantage in that situation.",
        "start": 660.56,
        "duration": 5.541
    },
    {
        "text": "And so you're asking:\n\"What's the catch?\"",
        "start": 666.126,
        "duration": 2.65
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 668.801,
        "duration": 0.554
    },
    {
        "text": "Or somebody tells you...",
        "start": 669.38,
        "duration": 1.616
    },
    {
        "text": "Your friend tells you:",
        "start": 671.021,
        "duration": 0.669
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Hey. I got this job, and they're going to\nsend me here and they're going to do this, and",
        "start": 671.715,
        "duration": 2.546
    },
    {
        "text": "they're going to do that, and\nthey're paying me so much money.\"",
        "start": 674.286,
        "duration": 2.12
    },
    {
        "text": "And it sounds like almost too good,\nso you say: \"What's the catch?\"",
        "start": 676.467,
        "duration": 5.188
    },
    {
        "text": "It's like: \"Oh, well, I have to do\nthis stuff which is not legal.\"",
        "start": 681.68,
        "duration": 3.542
    },
    {
        "text": "It was like: \"Oh, okay. Well,\nthen, you better not.\"",
        "start": 685.247,
        "duration": 3.059
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 688.331,
        "duration": 0.776
    },
    {
        "text": "So, there are all kinds of\nsituations in which we can use this.",
        "start": 689.132,
        "duration": 3.78
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 693.159,
        "duration": 0.59
    },
    {
        "text": "Now, let's try to match them up.",
        "start": 693.774,
        "duration": 2.699
    },
    {
        "text": "So which question can you use when you\nwant to say: \"Do you know each other?\"",
        "start": 696.974,
        "duration": 5.121
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 702.12,
        "duration": 0.711
    },
    {
        "text": "You have two friends: \"Do\nyou know each other?\"",
        "start": 702.856,
        "duration": 2.54
    },
    {
        "text": "What do we say?",
        "start": 705.573,
        "duration": 1.614
    },
    {
        "text": "Did you find it?",
        "start": 708.953,
        "duration": 1.469
    },
    {
        "text": "We asked: \"Have you met?\"",
        "start": 710.946,
        "duration": 2.312
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay? Good.",
        "start": 713.318,
        "duration": 1.475
    },
    {
        "text": "All right.",
        "start": 716.911,
        "duration": 0.805
    },
    {
        "text": "What's the hidden problem?",
        "start": 717.741,
        "duration": 2.22
    },
    {
        "text": "What's that hidden condition?",
        "start": 719.986,
        "duration": 2.502
    },
    {
        "text": "Which expression or\nquestion asks that?",
        "start": 723.571,
        "duration": 4.339
    },
    {
        "text": "It's here,",
        "start": 728.281,
        "duration": 2.114
    },
    {
        "text": "number 10. Right?",
        "start": 733.025,
        "duration": 1.728
    },
    {
        "text": "\"What's the catch?",
        "start": 734.778,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "What's the hidden problem?",
        "start": 735.964,
        "duration": 1.311
    },
    {
        "text": "What's the hidden disadvantage?\"",
        "start": 737.3,
        "duration": 2.628
    },
    {
        "text": "If you want to ask somebody:\n\"Do you understand?\"",
        "start": 740.649,
        "duration": 3.081
    },
    {
        "text": "what's another way\nwe can ask that?",
        "start": 743.755,
        "duration": 2.525
    },
    {
        "text": "Which one?",
        "start": 747.04,
        "duration": 1.319
    },
    {
        "text": "This one, it's:",
        "start": 749.28,
        "duration": 1.579
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Do you follow?\"",
        "start": 753.179,
        "duration": 1.991
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 755.195,
        "duration": 0.555
    },
    {
        "text": "Good.",
        "start": 755.75,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Are you going home already?\"",
        "start": 757.092,
        "duration": 1.839
    },
    {
        "text": "How can we ask that?",
        "start": 759.65,
        "duration": 1.73
    },
    {
        "text": "Do you know?",
        "start": 762.536,
        "duration": 1.499
    },
    {
        "text": "Yes, number six:",
        "start": 764.544,
        "duration": 2.51
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Leaving so soon?\" Okay?",
        "start": 767.82,
        "duration": 1.829
    },
    {
        "text": "Again, it doesn't mean\nyou're going home.",
        "start": 769.649,
        "duration": 1.98
    },
    {
        "text": "It's just an example.",
        "start": 771.629,
        "duration": 1.19
    },
    {
        "text": "You could be just leaving.",
        "start": 772.819,
        "duration": 1.411
    },
    {
        "text": "We don't know where\nthat person is going.",
        "start": 774.23,
        "duration": 2.536
    },
    {
        "text": "And the last one: \"What's happening?\", or\n\"What happened?\", or \"What's the latest?\",",
        "start": 777.089,
        "duration": 3.816
    },
    {
        "text": "or \"What's the story?\"",
        "start": 780.93,
        "duration": 1.94
    },
    {
        "text": "What's that one?",
        "start": 783.256,
        "duration": 1.294
    },
    {
        "text": "The one that's left, number\neight: \"What's the scoop?\"",
        "start": 786.199,
        "duration": 4.241
    },
    {
        "text": "All right?",
        "start": 790.557,
        "duration": 0.936
    },
    {
        "text": "So I hope that these 10 questions are easy\nenough-and I think they are-that you could",
        "start": 791.518,
        "duration": 7.356
    },
    {
        "text": "actually start using\nthem yourself.",
        "start": 798.899,
        "duration": 2.337
    },
    {
        "text": "It's important to understand them, but it's also\nimportant to start using the common expressions",
        "start": 801.261,
        "duration": 5.064
    },
    {
        "text": "that native speakers\nuse in everyday life.",
        "start": 806.35,
        "duration": 3.26
    },
    {
        "text": "So, if you'd like to practice this,\nplease go to our website: www.engvid.com.",
        "start": 809.821,
        "duration": 6.518
    },
    {
        "text": "There, first of all you can review\nthese by doing a quiz on our website.",
        "start": 816.364,
        "duration": 5.155
    },
    {
        "text": "You can also look around, because we have\nhundreds of other lessons on all kinds of",
        "start": 821.519,
        "duration": 5.26
    },
    {
        "text": "areas of English, like grammar and vocabulary,\nand writing, and exam prep, pronunciation,",
        "start": 826.804,
        "duration": 6.647
    },
    {
        "text": "everything you can imagine.",
        "start": 833.476,
        "duration": 1.716
    },
    {
        "text": "All right?",
        "start": 835.217,
        "duration": 0.795
    },
    {
        "text": "And also, if you\nhaven't already,",
        "start": 836.037,
        "duration": 2.721
    },
    {
        "text": "please subscribe to my YouTube\nchannel so you can continue",
        "start": 838.783,
        "duration": 3.017
    },
    {
        "text": "to get lots of videos and lessons for free\nthat will help you improve your English.",
        "start": 841.8,
        "duration": 5.529
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 847.329,
        "duration": 0.691
    },
    {
        "text": "Bye for now.",
        "start": 848.045,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Good luck with your English.",
        "start": 849.07,
        "duration": 1.214
    }
]